  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-AR-01 adversarial sample)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Full 13-factor assessment performed. Decision: Accepted. This package is a synthetic adversarial sample targeting W-AR-01: the Discretization error factor carries a requiredLevel of 4 with extensive narrative rationale but no structured acceptanceCriteria field, creating a credible appearance of documentation without the required structured link.",
